<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.8">
<l>koṅkumali karuṅkuvaḷai kaṇṇāka teṇkayaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>ceṅkamala mukamalarttun tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>vaṅkamali taṭaṅkaṭaluḷ variyaravi ṉaṇaittuyiṉṟā</l>
<l>ceṅkamala nāpaṉukki ḻantēṉeṉ ceṟivaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my clustered bangles to the one with a red lotus navel</l>
<l>Who sleeps on a striped serpent bed in the vast sea where waves swell,</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram where in clear pools</l>
<l>Bloom red lotus faces, while pollen-laden dark lilies become eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
